{"tid":257875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五年後冇本地海魚食？末代漁民：政府懶理我哋死活","createTime":"2017-05-25T15:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T01:30:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b14c91198181c7f932d5dbfce88db72091a6124","tid":257875,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017年5月25日<br />\n【飲食籽：追源尋味】<br />\n大陸休漁期開始，很多人以為香港會沒魚好吃，其實對於本地漁民，這時正正是捕魚黃金時期。休漁期南海海域少了拖魚，反而多了魚進入香港近岸海域，本地漁民便趁機捉新鮮海魚到市場賣，除了飛機貨和淡水魚外，讓我們有多一個選擇。一條魚得來不易，漁民要睇天做人，日曬雨淋，24小時候命。但漁業式微，仍堅持留下的已寥寥可數，2013年起政府不發新的捕魚證，本地漁業似已走到盡頭&hellip;&hellip;不妨花時間了解這班本地漁民，尋回香港這個漁村的根本。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OnuZvsAI1Ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOnuZvsAI1Ac&d=Fi3RlZIS89NrQIGLncg3OpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=aab827ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OnuZvsAI1Ac</a>"},{"pid":"2a64a8ffe26d8c6088898389a1e375967184747f","tid":257875,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"漁農界？"},{"pid":"557cc17cd93549df10f2e692f1de93f7f19b2fdd","tid":257875,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79e9ece6e686d58caa3494b0857f9be3192fb17","tid":257875,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漁農界？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce068080808a4120a6aaedfe28ee5ab7197a8b2f","tid":257875,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦  一年賠幾多錢比班水佬"},{"pid":"75c978620af54445c02e9509de880bf5a7b2df82","tid":257875,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":